    <p><strong>Advice for musicians on how to get the most out of the SxSW Music Conference.</strong></p>

<p>
This was actually an hour-long talk that included me proposing to my future wife in the audience, but SxSW was nice enough to edit it down to a 5-minute summary video.<br>
<br>
For the full version, including advice from many musicians, go to http://sivers.org/sxsw
